Module com.example.project4
Package com.example.project4

Class Pizza

java.lang.Object
com.example.project4.Pizza
All Implemented Interfaces:
Customizable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BBQChicken, BuildYourOwn, Deluxe, Meatzza
public abstract class Pizza extends Object implements Customizable
A class that stores information about a customizable pizza. Can add and remove the customizable pizza. Can set and get size of the customizable pizza. Can set and get crust of the customizable pizza. Can set and get topping list of the customizable pizza. Can get price of the customizable pizza
Author:
Anirudh Chauhan, Matthew Calora
